ccre.util

Class CLinkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.util.CAbstractList<T>
      • ccre.util.CLinkedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the element type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CCollection<T>, CList<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class CLinkedList<T>
extends CAbstractList<T>
    A linked list. This will perform in O(N) for lookups and sets not at endpoints, and O(N) for inserts and deletions that are not to the ends of the list. This implementation is a circular linked list using a sentinel node for the start and end of the list.
